{
  "stem": "23506.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So what happened is I went to-- to Lodz-- from Tuszyn to Lodz, and in Lodz I had neighbors that they moved to Lodz many years ago.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were very good friends of my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I went to them, and I said like this, listen, I need to get out of some this thing from the [? lombard. ?] And Israel [?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Levich ?] says he's going to leave here money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He didn't leave any money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Can you do something about it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So they said that they want to lend me the-- the marks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they had a Polish man-- he's a volksdeutsche-- who used to smuggle for them between Lodz and Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were doing-- knitting-- knitting sweaters and little boots.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Get me in touch with this man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The man came, and we decided on a price, whatever I'm going to [? call ?] to pay him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I gave him the certificate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the-- I don't remember what their name was-- those-- those people that they gave me the money.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I waited.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came back the next time-- next day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, well, I was just staying in front, and they closed the door.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They said to come tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My nose told me that it is not right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there I am like a Pollack in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I knew the address of the-- of the [? lombard. ?] And I go up there very early to be close to the window.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I can see if this-- if he comes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you know, I stayed at the window.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't see this man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they said that no more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were not giving out any more-- those things that were hawked there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I go back to-- to the friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
